{"tid":2222752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：我不希望因為有人批評你們的手段，結果就完全放棄你們相信的理念。","createTime":"2020-09-29T09:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:50:31.000Z","uid":271829,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"89ad0846445314e7d42e97009abd7e5914571014","tid":2222752,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"梁天琦：<br />\n相信和平抗爭的人、相信公民抗命的人，繼續公民抗命；相信佔馬路、相信絕食、相信罷交稅等等和平手段，繼續去做。<br />\n我鼓勵你們去做，我希望你們去做。<br />\n我不希望因為有人批評你們的手段，結果就完全放棄你們相信的理念。<br />\n同時間，相信勇武抗爭的人，一樣要繼續做。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AV18R2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAV18R2F.jpg&h=6f96ef8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fd1213e1893e864aaf86d252f1c17926a02fa1a","tid":2222752,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSHnL4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSHnL4h.jpg&h=30b430f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a328e28fe209bc1764b71c49859f3e595ab8740e","tid":2222752,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae1f7920f5b2f20c5146808666b20549f62891ed","tid":2222752,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fd1213e1893e864aaf86d252f1c17926a02fa1a","tid":2222752,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSHnL4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSHnL4h.jpg&h=30b430f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"屌你ID 5萬幾都係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457e5847b0a9d7bd5e183cdd0d425a46e815e6f7","tid":2222752,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1f7920f5b2f20c5146808666b20549f6289